## How it works
1. You deploy the bot with the **GitHub Action** (`.github/workflows/one-click-deploy.yml`).
2. In Teams, add the app to your target **group chat** (e.g., ŌĆ£CECS 1040 ŌĆō AI Literacy 2026ŌĆØ) and @mention it once ŌĆö this stores the chatŌĆÖs **conversation reference** in Azure Table Storage. A bot must be installed before it can proactively post to a chat; it canŌĆÖt create a chat on its own. ŅłĆciteŅłéturn2search38Ņłü
3. A timer trigger runs **daily** (default 01:00 UTC = 08:00 ICT) and posts an **Adaptive Card** with Top 3 AI news + 3 facts. You can change the schedule in `api/NewsTimer/function.json` or set `WEBSITE_TIME_ZONE` to interpret CRON in your local time. ŅłĆciteŅłéturn2search8Ņłü

